<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019834>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 70–74. Abdominal segment 8 of Atheta frosti Bernhauer (male, lectotype of At. modiella Casey (70–72); and female, lectotype of At. frosti (73–74)). 70 — male tergum 8; 71 — male sternum 8; 72 — apex of male tergum 8; 73 — female tergum 8; 74 — female sternum 8. Scale bar 0.1 mm (72), 0.2 mm (70–71, 73–74)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5019834/files/figure.png" .

